SPOTLIGHT WK 8

Hot off of last week's record-breaking LNRZ drop, we have another S-tier track made from the SATELLITES sample pack. Elcee weaves through this beat with supreme agility, keeping us on our toes every second. 

Here's what Elcee has to say about it:

"Every lyric in this song really happened...also we made this tune on discord, pattern up Xx"

Join LNRZ HQ here: https://guild.xyz/lnrz-hq

Visit our website: https://lnrz.xyz/
